sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant L as LLM
    participant M as MCP Tool
    participant G as GraphQL API

    U->>L: question
    L->>M: tool? (introspect | query)
    alt introspect
        M->>G: __schema
        G-->>M: schema
    else query
        M->>G: query
        G-->>M: data
    end
    M-->>L: result
    L-->>U: answer
